  "description": "A breathtaking sunset scene. The sky is ablaze with vibrant, horizontal bands of color ranging from fiery oranges and reds near the horizon to softer pinks and purples higher up. Dramatic cloud formations, appearing as wispy streaks, stretch across the sky, creating a sense of movement and depth. Below the sky, a dark silhouette of trees and vegetation forms the foreground, with the faint outline of a distant city and hills visible on the horizon. The overall effect is one of natural beauty and tranquility.",
